/chopped-wedge-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1767w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-728x907.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-768x956.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-1233x1536.jpg 1233w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-1645x2048.jpg 1645w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-150x187.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1767px) 100vw, 1767px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201767%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1767w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-728x907.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-768x956.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-1233x1536.jpg 1233w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-1645x2048.jpg 1645w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-150x187.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-6-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe vinaigrette keeps the salad feeling a little lighter. It also keeps the bacon crisp and the iceberg crisp as well! It’s not drenched in a creamy dressing which gives it a little bit of staying power. Plus – the flavor. Ohhhh the flavor. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI am a nut and could probably drink this dressing. At least take a spoonful of it! \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-99826\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chopped wedge salad\" width=\"1704\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chopped Wedge Salad with Blue Cheese Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1704w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-728x940.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-768x992.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-1189x1536.jpg 1189w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-1586x2048.jpg 1586w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1704px) 100vw, 1704px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201704%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1704w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-728x940.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-768x992.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-1189x1536.jpg 1189w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-1586x2048.jpg 1586w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe nice thing about this chopped salad is that you don’t have to do a ton of work to get those even sized pieces. The bacon is already in crumbles. The iceberg falls apart as you slice. The tomatoes are really the only ingredient that takes some chopping work: quarter or halve them depending on their size. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEverything goes into one bowl, tossed in the dressing and boom! It’s done.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chopped wedge salad\" width=\"1644\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chopped Wedge Salad with Blue Cheese Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg 1644w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-728x974.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-1531x2048.jpg 1531w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-150x201.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1644px) 100vw, 1644px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201644%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg 1644w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-728x974.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-1531x2048.jpg 1531w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-150x201.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOn a super hot day, I could eat this for dinner. It’s a great BBQ salad. Also an excellent side salad or a potluck dish – just drizzle on the dressing right before serving. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eP.S. the vinaigrette makes a little extra, and you can use it on EVERYTHING. Chicken, steak, veggies, pasta salads, grilled bread – the works.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chopped wedge salad\" width=\"1692\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chopped Wedge Salad with Blue Cheese Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-scaled.jpg 1692w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-728x947.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-768x999.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-1181x1536.jpg 1181w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-1575x2048.jpg 1575w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-150x195.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1692px) 100vw, 1692px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201692%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-scaled.jpg 1692w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-728x947.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-768x999.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-1181x1536.jpg 1181w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-1575x2048.jpg 1575w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-150x195.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-12-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eChopped Wedge Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-99843\" data-recipe-id=\"99843\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-11-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eChopped Wedge Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99843\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI love a chopped wedge salad! All the classic flavors of a wedge: iceberg, tomatoes, crispy bacon and chives with a wonderful blue cheese vinaigrette. Super delicious and so easy to make!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-99843-ingredients\" data-recipe=\"99843\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eslices\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/applegate-natural-uncured-sunday-bacon-8oz/-/A-14871957?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebacon,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ehead iceberg lettuce,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/premium-cherry-tomatoes-10oz-good-38-gather-8482-packaging-may-vary/-/A-82667108?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echerry tomatoes,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecrumbled blue cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped fresh chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003eblue cheese vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pompeian-gourmet-white-wine-vinegar-16-fl-oz/-/A-50295901?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ewhite wine vinegar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic clove,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-dill-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495117?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efresh dill\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-clover-honey-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54436198?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ehoney\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/dijon-mustard-12oz-market-pantry-8482/-/A-14766261?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edijon mustard\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"13\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003epinch\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eof salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"14\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"15\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3 to 4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecrumbled blue cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-99843-instructions\" data-recipe=\"99843\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99843-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the chopped bacon in a skillet over medium heat. Cook, stirring often, until the bacon is crispy and the fat is rendered. Remove the bacon with a slotted spoon and place it on a paper towel to drain excess grease.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99843-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eChop up the head of iceberg lettuce and place it in a bowl. Toss with a big pinch of salt and pepper. Add in the cherry tomatoes, bacon and blue cheese. Drizzle with a few spoonfuls of the dressing and toss. Sprinkle on the fresh chives.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99843-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eServe with extra dressing for drizzling!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003eblue cheese vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99843-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhisk together the vinegar, garlic, chives, honey and dijon. Stream in the olive oil while whisking until emulsified. Stir in the blue cheese. This stays great in the fridge for 2 to 3 days.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSalad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chopped wedge salad\" width=\"1644\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chopped Wedge Salad with Blue Cheese Vinaigrette.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-scaled.jpg 1644w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-728x974.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-1531x2048.jpg 1531w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chopped-wedge-salad-9-150x201.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1644px) 100vw, 1644px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%2